The updates of COVID-19 in Republic of Korea
As of 24 February,2020


○ Compared to yesterday morning (09:00, 23 February, 2020), 207 additional cases are confirmed, which brings the total number of confirmed cases to 763 with 738 cases in isolation. 19,127 turned out to be negative and 8,725 are currently being tested. 
 




