  * The 9th, 13th, 15th, and 20th cases will be released from isolation later today.
**  Three cases(#54, #55, and #286) passed away on 23 February, and the cause of death is currently being investigated. 54th case is a Korean male born in 1963, 55th case is a Korean male born in 1961, and 286th case is a Korean male born in 1958. All of the deceased cases belong to Cheongdo Daenam Hospital cluster.

○ Including 207 newly confirmed cases, the total of 763 cases are classified by the clusters and the regions as follows.
 




